text: The Partner is a 1963 British drama movie directed by Gerard Glaister and was based on the 1926 novel of the same name by Edgar Wallace. It stars Yoko Tani, Guy Doleman, Ewan Roberts, Mark Eden, Anthony Booth, John Forgeham and Virginia Wetherell. ==Other websites== * Category:1963 drama movies Category:British drama movies Category:Movies based on books
title: The Partner (1963 movie)
